{
  "text": "This is likely to be due to the increased probability of suffering injuries while engaging in sports. An alternative explanation is that those participating in sports are more health conscious or are required to have regular physical check-ups. People with higher incomes 13 Details can be found in [CITATION_1] or in the extended version of this paper.",
